OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FEasternmost
OL,6,Fparts of the region may catch a shower
OL,7,Fearly this evening, but for most it
OL,8,Fwill be dry with sunny, then clear
OL,9,Fperiods. Overnight, some low cloud
OL,10,Fwill edge in from the east, bringing
OL,11,Fpatchy drizzle and hill fog.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FA bright start across
OL,14,FCornwall, but on the whole Tuesday
OL,15,Fwill be a cloudy day, with patchy
OL,16,Fdrizzle and some hill fog initially.
OL,17,FSkies generally brightening up towards
OL,18,Fthe evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
