OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FWest
OL,6,FDevon and Cornwall could see showers
OL,7,Fon Wednesday and Thursday. Otherwise
OL,8,Fmostly sunny, though windy for a time
OL,9,Fwith coastal gales. Showers extending
OL,10,Feastwards on Friday, though winds
OL,11,Flighter.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
